  "body": "### Description\r\nAs an operator, I want full block hashes so that I can grep for them in logs and display them in Splunk dashboards. \r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce (Bug)\r\n1. Run a sync\r\n2. Grep for FullImportBlockStep\r\n3. See that log lines look like \"Import reached block 3787200 (0xa147..ad3d), 29.996 Mg/s, Peers: 25\"\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior:**\r\nShould see full block hash in parens\r\n\r\n**Actual behavior:**\r\nOnly see the beginning and end of the hash, making it useless to match block hashes.\r\n\r\n### Versions (Add all that apply)\r\n* Software version: 20.10.1\r\n\r\n\r\n",
